PHP Code:
wuxing_gu={ --无形蛊
fastwalkrun_p={{{1,-10},{25,-50},{26,-50}},{{1,18*2},{20,18*2}}}
},
Sửa lại thành:
PHP Code:
wuxing_gu={ --无形蛊
fastwalkrun_p={{{1,-10},{25,-50},{26,-50}},{{1,18*2},{20,18*2}}},
poisondamage_v={
[1]={{1,5},{20,25}},
[2]={{1,20},{20,20}},
[3]={{1,25},{2,25}}
}
},

